title: New: Angel Haze – Shit I Don’t Like
content:
Angel Haze has managed to squeeze an impressive stint into the end of 2012. Her collaboration with the producer Lunice was perhaps a highlight, a grandiose, stonking jam that cemented her as a firm ‘on to watch’ in 2013. In a year that started with Azealia Banks, it’s encouraging to see a female MC end the year with a bit more substance. Her new cut/demo sees her take on Chief Keef’s ‘I don’t like’. Her flow is quick, sharp and as always, firmly on point.

2013: the year of Angel Haze.
